      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. GETTING CHEEKY trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5 lengths into second (20.09) at Angle Park in a TG1-4W over 342m. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Overdue and expected to feature again. 4. STELLA SWIFT has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when second (19.86) in a Grade 6 at Angle Park. Can feature with the right run. 1. PHYLLOXERA FURY finds it hard to break through. Finished third (17.30) at Murray Bridge Straight latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Expected to feature. 6. BEN LIKES SCOTCH has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.\",\"runners\":[2,4,1,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
